      • Invoice

        public Invoice(int oNum,
       java.lang.String oDate,
       double total,
       int quantity,
       java.lang.String pDate,
       java.lang.String cCode,
       java.lang.String stat,
       java.lang.String custInfo)
        Parameters:
        oNum - represents the invoice number
        oDate - represents the date of the order
        total - represents the total price of the order
        quantity - shows the amount of items purchased within an order
        pDate - represents the date the order was completely paid for
        cCode - indicates the company code used to pay for the order
        stat - represents the current status of the order
        custInfo - represents the current customer info. This method is the Invoice object overloaded constructor. It allows for the creation of a user-created invoices
